Package ua.pp.ihorzak.alog

Interface ALogFormatterComplexDelegate<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Class of instances which can be transformed to logging string using this class instances.
    public interface ALogFormatterComplexDelegate<T>
    ALogFormatter delegate that is responsible for custom specified class instances transformation to string for logging. This class differs from ALogFormatterDelegate by providing of helper delegate instance for logging string transformation of target object contained objects. Should be used for ALogFormatter creation via ALogFormatter.create(ALogFormatterComplexDelegate).
